description: This 2024 fully renovated top floor duplex condo offers 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and a large composite private deck. Spanning 1,452 square feet across two floors, this home exudes a true sense of spaciousness and comfort. Step into the brand-new chef’s kitchen featuring custom cabinetry, Bosch & Sharp appliances, and quartz countertops. Hardwood floors grace the entire home, complemented by Central AC & heat, tankless hot water system, and exquisite custom trim & tile details throughout. The main level boasts a primary bedroom with an en suite bath, an additional full bath conveniently located near the in-unit washer/dryer, and an expansive living & dining area perfect for gatherings. Upstairs, discover two well-appointed bedrooms, another full bath, and ample closet space. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to own a beautiful new home in South Boston!
